{"type": "article", "id": 7269, "title": "Junya Watanabe 2015 秋冬系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-11T07:21:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234255kBjoihE9CaNWn8OT.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t日本服装设计师 Junya Watanabe 在巴黎时装周上展示了其品牌 2015 秋冬系列，这个由川保久玲一手捧红的设计师如今越来越前卫了，这次他让模特们把一堆立体的几何形状穿在了身上。这些立体的几何形状大多是自然界常见的数学形状，比如钻石样式。有的看起来酷酷的，有的看起来模特像是把一个纸灯笼套在了头上。这里没有链接，因为你肯定只是看看日本人的奇思妙想，肯定不会下单买的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234253DgeaXiJ1OEY7KBIR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.31623932\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234254gwGrJQm53CMKSYdx.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.43589744\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234254hsCQY0RWLFbSytux.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.46153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234254RhcVG3MQzebi4jpF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.51709402\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052342554FYGuNO7RDWicd3E.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.44444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}